---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now"
  description="Current work, interests, and what has my attention right now."
  currentPath="/now"
>
  <section class="content-body">
    <span class="eyebrow">Now</span>
    <h1>Current Work</h1>
    <p>
      This page is a snapshot of what I am actively doing rather than a polished bio.
      It changes when the work changes.
    </p>
    <h2>Primary Focus</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Shipping small internal tools with less ceremony and tighter feedback loops.</li>
      <li>Improving deployment safety with simpler build and release steps.</li>
      <li>Publishing more technical notes instead of letting them die in private docs.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Side Interests</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Static sites and content systems that stay readable after a year.</li>
      <li>Unix-heavy workflows, terminal tooling, and durable local-first setups.</li>
      <li>Design that feels intentional without looking over-produced.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
